sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant B as Browser
    participant NX as Nginx (login-frontend)
    participant LF as Login Page
    participant IAM as IAM Mock

    B->>NX: GET /
    NX->>LF: Serve login.html
    LF-->>B: Login Form

    B->>NX: POST /api/authenticate<br/>(Basic Auth)
    NX->>IAM: POST /authenticate<br/>(Basic Auth)
    Note over IAM: Validate credentials<br/>Issue JWT (sub, role, exp)
    IAM-->>NX: { token, userId, role }
    NX-->>B: { token, userId, role }

    Note over B: Store JWT in sessionStorage

    alt Role = doctor
        B->>NX: GET /producer/
        Note over NX: Proxy to producer-frontend:80
        NX-->>B: Producer Frontend SPA
    else Role = patient
        B->>NX: GET /consumer/
        Note over NX: Proxy to consumer-frontend:80
        NX-->>B: Consumer Frontend SPA
    end
